018package org.apache.hadoop.hbase;
019
020import org.apache.yetus.audience.InterfaceAudience;
021
022/**
023 * POJO to present Unknown Regions from Catalog Janitor Inconsistencies Report via REST API. These
024 * inconsistencies are shown on hbck.jsp page on Active HMaster UI as part of Catalog Janitor
025 * inconsistencies.
026 */
027@InterfaceAudience.Public
028public class HbckUnknownServers {
029  private final HbckRegionDetails regionInfo;
030  private final HbckServerName serverName;
031
032  public HbckUnknownServers(HbckRegionDetails regionInfo, HbckServerName unknownServerName) {
033    this.regionInfo = regionInfo;
034    this.serverName = unknownServerName;
035  }
036
037  public HbckRegionDetails getRegionInfo() {
038    return regionInfo;
039  }
040
041  public HbckServerName getServerName() {
042    return serverName;
043  }
044}
